Optimization update:
Pollution data storage type changed from double (64 bits) to float (32 bits), thus reducing the memory usage;
Optimized WorldProcessingThread's work;
Small pollution values(lower than 5.0, by default) are being cleared from memory, reducing RAM and disk memory usage;
Fixed smog and acid rain renderers when DynamicSurroundings are installed.
